PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmurder of an 18-year-old University of
OL,8,FSouthampton student by stabbing him to
OL,9,Fdeath with a Sikh kirpan ceremonial
OL,10,Fknife.
OL,12,FVickrum Digwa told police a "wicked
OL,13,Flie" that he was the victim of a
OL,14,Fracist attack, after he stabbed
OL,15,Ffinance student Henry Nowak, from
OL,16,FChaffod Hundred, Essex, five times
OL,17,Fwith a 21cm blade.
OL,19,FThe incident took place in Belmont
OL,20,FRoad, Southampton, on December 3, 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
