OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FDigwa was filmed by his victim telling
OL,7,Fhim "I am a bad man" moments before
OL,8,Fthe knife attack, which included two
OL,9,Fstab wounds to the back of Mr Nowak's
OL,10,Flegs and a fatal wound to his heart.
OL,12,FThe 23-year-old was also convicted of
OL,13,Fcarrying a bladed weapon in public.
OL,14,FHis mother, Kiran Kaur, 53, was found
OL,15,Fguilty of assisting an offender by
OL,16,Fremoving a weapon from the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FGiving evidence, the defendant told
OL,7,Fthe court that Mr Nowak, who he
OL,8,Fdescribed as drunk, had racially
OL,9,Fabused him before punching him and
OL,10,Fknocking his turban off.
OL,12,FHe said he stabbed Mr Nowak to the
OL,13,Fback of his legs in self-defence,
OL,14,Fafter the teenager had threatened him
OL,15,Fand grabbed him by the hair.
OL,17,FDigwa claimed he had not realised at
OL,18,Fthe time he had caused the fatal stab
OL,19,Fwound to his chest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FBut the prosecution said Digwa had
OL,7,F"lied" to police who attended the
OL,8,Fscene, telling them he had been the
OL,9,Fvictim of a racist attack.
OL,11,FHe also deceived officers by claiming
OL,12,Fthat he had not stabbed Mr Nowak
OL,13,Fdespite the student's pleas for help
OL,14,Fas he told the police that he was
OL,15,Finjured.
OL,17,FThis led officers to arrest Mr Nowak
OL,18,Fand place him in handcuffs moments
OL,19,Fbefore he collapsed and became
OL,20,Funconscious.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
