PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FHe died despite their best efforts to
OL,7,Fgive him first aid.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FTech billionaire Elon Musk had posted
OL,15,Fon X an offer to fund a private
OL,16,Fprosecution against the police.
OL,18,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct (IOPC), meanwhile, is
OL,20,Finvestigating the circumstances of the
OL,21,Fincident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FFollowing the case, Hampshire Police
OL,7,FDeputy Chief Constable Robert France
OL,8,Fapologised on behalf of the officers,
OL,9,Fbut said they were 'lied to" and would
OL,10,Fhave been unaware of Mr Nowak's
OL,11,Finjury, which he said would not have
OL,12,Fbeen obvious.
OL,14,FHe said: "This is an absolutely tragic
OL,15,Fcase, and my sympathies are absolutely
OL,16,Fwith Henry's family, his friends, and
OL,17,Fhis loved ones.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,F"I want to apologise, I want to say
OL,7,Fthat I am sorry that Henry couldn't be
OL,8,Fsaved that night. I'm sorry that he
OL,9,Fwas handcuffed and arrested in the
OL,10,Fmoments before he lost consciousness."
OL,12,FNicholas Lobbenberg KC, prosecuting,
OL,13,Ftold the jury that Digwa, who had been
OL,14,Ftraining with weapons since the age of
OL,15,F12, had described the murder weapon in
OL,16,F"loving terms" and that he "sleeps in
OL,17,Fa bedroom with an arsenal of weapons".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FHe also said that although Sikhs are
OL,7,Fpermitted in law to carry a kirpan
OL,8,Fknife, the discrete carrying of a
OL,9,Fsmall dagger under clothing was
OL,10,Fsufficient for the requirements of the
OL,11,Freligion.
OL,13,FHe said the defendant "chose" to carry
OL,14,Ftwo knives, one under his clothing
OL,15,Fwhile the large knife which was used
OL,16,Fin the killing was on display.
OL,18,FHe added: "This is a man who likes
OL,19,Fweapons. He thinks a knife is a
OL,20,Fsuitable wedding present for his
OL,21,Fbrother."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FThe Sikh Federation UK said the death
OL,7,Fwas an "isolated incident" and it was
OL,8,Fraising awareness of the rules around
OL,9,Fthe carrying of a kirpan.
OL,11,FIn a statement, it said: "The wider
OL,12,FSikh community has unacceptably faced
OL,13,Fconsiderable abuse and hate during the
OL,14,Ftrial as many do not understand the
OL,15,Flaw, the significance of the kirpan or
OL,16,Fthe responsibility associated with
OL,17,Fwearing a kirpan.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,F"The actions of police officers who
OL,7,Fhandcuffed the victim just before he
OL,8,Fdied has not helped and given an
OL,9,Fopportunity for many to criticise the
OL,10,Fpolice, but it has also unnecessarily
OL,11,Fstirred up community hatred.
OL,13,F"Now the trial is over we want to make
OL,14,Fabsolutely clear the law only provides
OL,15,Ffully practising Sikhs with a defence
OL,16,Funder the law to wear a kirpan for
OL,17,Freligious reasons."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,FPaying tribute to Mr Nowak, his family
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement released after his
OL,8,Fdeath that he had been "fully
OL,9,Fembracing university life" and had
OL,10,Fbeen out with his football team-mates
OL,11,Fon the night of his death.
OL,13,FDescribing him as "our kind,
OL,14,Fintelligent and talented son", they
OL,15,Fadded: "Henry was loved by all those
OL,16,Fthat knew him.
OL,18,F"Our hearts ache when we think of the
OL,19,Fbright future he had ahead of him,
OL,20,Ffull of opportunity and adventures.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780034663
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,CSouthampton University student
OL,6,F"There are no words to describe just
OL,7,Fhow heartbroken we are that we will
OL,8,Fnever get to see him grow and fulfil
OL,9,Fhis awesome potential.
OL,11,F"We are so proud of him and all he
OL,12,Fachieved.
OL,14,F"Our world will never be the same
OL,15,Fwithout our amazing Henry."
OL,17,FJudge William Mousley KC adjourned the
OL,18,Fcase for Digwa to be sentenced on June
OL,19,F1 and Kaur on July 17.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
